rder-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"55\"><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">9.&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"142\"><p><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px\">农业部华南动物营养与饲料科学观测实验站</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"120\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px\">动物科学学院</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"110\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px\">2011.7</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"86\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px\">江青艳</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"95\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px\">农业部</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:62px\"><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"55\"><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">10.&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-left: 1px solid;\" valign=\"center\" width=\"142\"><p><span style=\";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font