-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">广东省农田土壤污染修复工程技术研究中心</span></p></td><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-left-color: currentColor;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"118\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">李永涛</span></p></td><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-left-color: currentColor;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"234\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">资源环境学院</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 20px;\"><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"51\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">2</span></p></td><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-left-color: currentColor;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"374\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">广东省环境友好型肥料工程技术研究中心</span></p></td><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-left-color: currentColor;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"118\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 19px;\">樊小林</span></p></td><td class=\"selectTdClass\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 7px; border-left-color: currentColor;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"234\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-h